<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:08:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾海岸警卫队称船只与中国船只相撞受损</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-coast-guard-says-ship-damaged-in-collision-with-chinese-vessel/articleshow/108222107.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108222107.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾海岸警卫队表示，周二，其一艘船只在南海一个偏远前哨基地向菲律宾军队执行补给任务时与一艘中国海岸警卫队船只相撞，造成损坏。菲律宾海岸警卫队准将杰伊·塔里拉(Jay Tarriela)在社交媒体平台上发帖称，中国海警和其他船只进行了“危险的机动和拦截”，导致碰撞，导致“菲律宾海岸警卫队(PCG)船只受到轻微结构性损坏”。 X。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-coast-guard-says-ship-damaged-in-collision-with-chinese-vessel/articleshow/108222107.cms</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装部长表示，进入也门水域的船只必须获得许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ships-entering-yemeni-waters-must-obtain-permit-houthi-minister-says/articleshow/108221911.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221911.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;胡塞武装海事管理局要求船只进入也门水域获得许可证。胡塞武装分子袭击国际航运以声援巴勒斯坦人。美国和英国以爆炸回应。也门的命令影响了曼德海峡的领海，这对全球航运至关重要。也门冲突自 2014 年以来一直持续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:48:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ships-entering-yemeni-waters-must-obtain-permit-houthi-minister-says/articleshow/108221911.cms</guid></item><item><title>平壤警告美韩演习后果</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pyongyang-warns-of-consequences-over-us-south-korea-drills/articleshow/108221936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜周二表示，首尔和华盛顿将为本周开始的大规模军事演习付出“高昂代价”，并敦促盟国停止“疯狂的战争演习”。华盛顿和首尔表示，华盛顿和首尔周一开始举行年度春季军事演习，参加演习的部队人数比 2023 年增加了一倍，以加强应对平壤不断升级的核威胁的准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pyongyang-warns-of-consequences-over-us-south-korea-drills/articleshow/108221936.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚推定总统普拉博沃承诺“非常顺利”的权力过渡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-promises-very-smooth-transition-of-power/articleshow/108221619.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221619.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普拉博沃·苏比安托承诺平稳权力交接，延续维多多的政策，目标是实现 8% 的经济增长。寻求私有化、提高税率、创造就业机会、粮食自给自足、投资、财政纪律。考虑投票率、粮食出口、民主、佐科维的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-promises-very-smooth-transition-of-power/articleshow/108221619.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普在超级星期二投票前赢得北达科他州党团会议胜利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wins-north-dakota-caucus-ahead-of-super-tuesday-vote/articleshow/108219651.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108219651.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普赢得北达科他州共和党总统预选，加强了他对该党提名的控制。他轻松击败了妮基·哈利。预计特朗普将在周二的选举中占据主导地位，重点关注可能与乔·拜登的大选重赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wins-north-dakota-caucus-ahead-of-super-tuesday-vote/articleshow/108219651.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平加强军力建设，中国国防预算增加7.2%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/as-xi-jinping-pursues-military-buildup-china-hikes-defense-budget-by-7-2/articleshow/108219325.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108219325.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国已超越其他国家，拥有世界上舰船数量最多的海军，并继续扩大其航母舰队。它与美国和俄罗斯并列，是唯一生产第五代战斗机的国家之一。然而，尽管中国取得了快速进步，包括美国称其以“惊人的速度”增强的太空军事能力，但中国仍面临内部挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/as-xi-jinping-pursues-military-buildup-china-hikes-defense-budget-by-7-2/articleshow/108219325.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称已对仁爱礁菲律宾船只采取措施</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-at-second-thomas-shoal/articleshow/108219447.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108219447.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国海警对非法侵入南海仁爱礁和仁爱礁附近争议海域的菲律宾船只采取管控措施。正在为驻扎在一艘搁浅军舰上的部队执行补给任务。尽管2016年的裁决称其主张没有法律依据，但中国仍声称对南海大部分地区拥有主权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-at-second-thomas-shoal/articleshow/108219447.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国称2024年国防开支将增长7.2%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-2024-defence-spending-to-rise-7-2/articleshow/108218645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-2024-defence-spending-to-rise-7-2/articleshow/108218645.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国空军雇员被指控在在线约会网站上分享机密信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-air-force-employee-accused-of-sharing-classified-information-on-online-dating-website/articleshow/108218543.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218543.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国司法部周一表示，美国空军雇员大卫·富兰克林·斯莱特因与他在外国在线约会平台上认识的一名女子泄露机密国防信息而被捕。斯莱特于周五在内布拉斯加州因三项联邦起诉书被拘留，预计将于周二首次出庭。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-air-force-employee-accused-of-sharing-classified-information-on-online-dating-website/articleshow/108218543.cms</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿州和爱达荷州分别发生雪崩，造成 2 名雪地摩托司机丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-snowmobilers-killed-in-separate-avalanches-in-washington-and-idaho/articleshow/108218982.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218982.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;华盛顿州和爱达荷州分别发生雪崩，两名雪地摩托车手丧生。据西北雪崩中心称，在华盛顿州亚基马，达兰德山附近的喀斯喀特山脉中，骑手引发了滑坡。在爱达荷州，一名雪地摩托车手在塞尔扣克山脉南部丧生。已故的雪地摩托车手被确认为来自爱达荷州桑德波因特的兰斯·吉德利 (Lance J. Gidley)。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-snowmobilers-killed-in-separate-avalanches-in-washington-and-idaho/articleshow/108218982.cms</guid></item><item><title>被指控的五角大楼泄密者认罪，面临近 17 年监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accused-pentagon-leaker-pleads-guilty-faces-almost-17-years-jail/articleshow/108218541.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218541.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;这名美国飞行员被指控在网上发布大量五角大楼高度机密文件，周一在联邦法院认罪。作为谈判协议的一部分，他同意被判处约 17 年监禁，作为交换，检察官同意撤销更严厉的间谍指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:30:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accused-pentagon-leaker-pleads-guilty-faces-almost-17-years-jail/articleshow/108218541.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列和联合国贸易指控“恐怖主义”和酷刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-un-trade-allegations-of-terrorism-torture/articleshow/108218522.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218522.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于处理 10 月 7 日袭击期间哈马斯武装分子性侵犯指控的问题引发紧张局势，以色列于周一召回了驻联合国大使。以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹因不断升级的争端而被召回进行磋商，他表示，“联合国花了五个月的时间才最终承认 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀期间犯下的性犯罪。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-un-trade-allegations-of-terrorism-torture/articleshow/108218522.cms</guid></item><item><title>“有理由相信”哈马斯袭击期间发生的强奸事件：联合国报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/grounds-to-believe-rapes-committed-during-hamas-attacks-un-report/articleshow/108218422.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218422.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国周一的一份报告称，有“合理的理由相信”哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列期间发生了强奸事件，随后被劫持到加沙的人质也遭到强奸。报告称：“调查小组发现，有合理的理由相信，10 月 7 日袭击期间，多个地点发生了与冲突有关的性暴力，包括强奸和轮奸。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/grounds-to-believe-rapes-committed-during-hamas-attacks-un-report/articleshow/108218422.cms</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处负责人警告全球和平与安全受到严重影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-chief-warns-of-serious-implications-for-global-peace-security/articleshow/108218368.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218368.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-chief-warns-of-serious-implications-for-global-peace-security/articleshow/108218368.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在与内塔尼亚胡竞争对手的会谈中对加沙局势表示“深切关注”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-vp-kamala-harris-expresses-deep-concerns-over-gaza-situation-in-talks-with-netanyahu-rival/articleshow/108217004.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108217004.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周一在与以色列战时内阁成员、总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的头号竞争对手本尼·甘茨的会谈中对加沙平民面临的局势表示“深切关注”。甘茨加入了 10 月 7 日后组建的五人战时内阁，旨在促进该国的团结。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-vp-kamala-harris-expresses-deep-concerns-over-gaza-situation-in-talks-with-netanyahu-rival/articleshow/108217004.cms</guid></item><item><title>首先，法国将堕胎列为宪法权利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-first-france-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right/articleshow/108216087.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216087.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:59:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-first-france-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right/articleshow/108216087.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国向马尔代夫提供无偿军事援助；签署协议以加强双边关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-provide-free-military-assistance-to-maldives-inks-agreement-to-bolster-bilateral-ties/articleshow/108216080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国和马尔代夫签署了防务合作协议，中国提供无偿军事援助以加强双边关系。该协议由马尔代夫国防部长穆罕默德·加桑·穆蒙和中国少将张宝群签署。这一事态发展是在马尔代夫为第一批印度军事人员撤出该国设定最后期限之后发生的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:54:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-provide-free-military-assistance-to-maldives-inks-agreement-to-bolster-bilateral-ties/articleshow/108216080.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国出人意料地取消总理年度新闻发布会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-scraps-premiers-annual-news-conference-in-surprise-move/articleshow/108216071.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216071.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国总理将不再在年度全国人大会议后举行新闻发布会。这一决定反映了中国日益增加的信息不透明度和习近平权力的巩固。政府对透明度和营造友好商业环境的承诺遭到破坏。与下级官员的问答环节将取代新闻发布会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-scraps-premiers-annual-news-conference-in-surprise-move/articleshow/108216071.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国和俄罗斯因乌克兰导弹音频泄露发生争执</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216041.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国政府否认了有关俄罗斯公布德国高级军官泄露的谈话内容暗示柏林正在准备对俄罗斯开战的指控。虽然德国当局没有质疑录音的真实性，但德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，将这些武器运送到乌克兰并不是一种选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</guid></item><item><title>苹果在 Spotify 案中被欧盟罚款 20 亿美元，将上诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108215933.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟委员会因不公平的交易条件以及阻止 Spotify 向用户告知 App Store 之外的支付选项而对苹果公司处以 18.4 亿欧元的罚款。苹果计划对这一决定提出质疑，并寻求解决另一项欧盟反垄断调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>